## lz — landing-zone-engine

**Namespace:** `lz` | **Propietario:** Team Landing Zone

| Métrica | Tipo | Unidad | Atributos | SLO |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `lz.files.processed.total` | Counter | `{file}` | `workspace.id`, `file.type`, `status` | Correctness 99.5% (28d) |
| `lz.file.processing.duration` | Histogram | `s` | `workspace.id`, `file.type` | Latency p99 < 300s |
| `lz.executions.active` | UpDownCounter | `{execution}` | `workspace.id` | Saturation |
| `lz.connection.errors.total` | Counter | `{error}` | `workspace.id`, `exception.type`, `connection.type` | Error rate |
| `lz.validation.errors.total` | Counter | `{error}` | `workspace.id`, `exception.type` | Correctness |

**Cardinalidad estimada:**

| Atributo | Valores |
|---|---|
| `workspace.id` | < 500 |
| `file.type` | `csv`, `xlsx`, `json`, `xml`, `txt` (5-10) |
| `status` | `success`, `failure`, `timeout` (3) |
| `exception.type` | `timeout`, `validation_error`, `parse_error`, `auth_error` (5-30) |
| `connection.type` | `sftp`, `api`, `s3`, `email` (5-10) |

